#  NOTE: OTP send/verify is intentionally mocked on the frontend
#        (no SMS gateway yet). The test OTP is always "123456".
#        See src/api/appointmentApi.js — MOCK START/END blocks.
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080   # uncomment if proxy is not used
